    "There are other Text-to-SQL models that use retrieval-augmentation generation (RAG) to provide examples dynamically.",
    "Guo et al. (2023b) presented an approach to enhance the generation of SQL queries from natural language questions, employing RAG in the prompts and a dynamic revision chain.",
